329
00:17:15,836 --> 00:17:18,336
The trap that the culprit used taking advantage

330
00:17:18,336 --> 00:17:20,436
of how the alarm system works.

331
00:17:20,436 --> 00:17:23,836
Look on top of that radiator.

332
00:17:23,836 --> 00:17:27,336
There is an unglazed pottery planter on it, isn't there?

